# Data Schema

Topic JSON files in `public/data/` follow the schema in `src/types/index.ts`.

## Adding a New Topic

1. Create `public/data/{topicId}.json` following the `Topic` interface
2. Add entry to `public/data/topics.json` (TopicMeta fields)
3. No code changes required — the app auto-discovers via topics.json

## ContentBlock Types

Each Section contains `content: ContentBlock[]`. Valid types:
`fact`, `text`, `table`, `stat_grid`, `comparison`, `range_bar`, `bar_chart`, `timeline`, `progress_stack`

Each type has its own required fields — check the discriminated union in `src/types/index.ts`.

## Conventions

- `id` fields: kebab-case (`status-quo`, `foerderung-2026`)
- `icon` field in TopicMeta: MUI icon name as string
- `lastUpdated`: format `YYYY-MM`
- Sources: always include `label`, `url` is optional
- Arguments: `keywords` array enables search matching, `relatedSections` links to section IDs
